ind.title: Ahli Gizi
ind.prompt: As a dietitian, I would like to design a vegetarian recipe for 2 people that has approximate 500 calories per serving and has a low glycemic index. The entire conversation and instructions should be provided in Indonesian. Can you please provide a suggestion?.
ind.description: Sebagai ahli diet, saya ingin merancang resep vegetarian untuk [target] yang memiliki [persyaratan]. Bisakah Anda memberikan saran?

metaDescription: Butuh template kontrak? Buat draft kontrak dengan syarat dan ketentuan standar!
